description:
Manual games allow you to set custom check locations and custom item names that will be rolled into a multiworld.
In this case the game from 2019: OuterWilds 
the player must manually refrain from using these gathered items until the tracker shows that they have been acquired or sent.

vE1.0.0-pre1.description:
PreRelease Untested (past generation) of the Echoes of the Eyes eddition of the rando appworld
attached to this apworld is 2 yaml, 

1. standard difficulty
2. force progression on Solanum and Prisonner Vault
vE1.0.0-pre1.title: EYE Apworld vpre1 UNTESTED

vE1.0.0-pre2.description:
PreRelease (in testing) of the Echoes of the Eyes eddition of the rando appworld
attached to this apworld is 2 yaml,
CHANGELOG:
\* renamed all the locations to replace the 2 letter prefix with the planet order.
\+ added some forgotten locations
\+ added a second copy of the meditation item to get it hopefully earlier
\* redid the regions requirements and connections
\* clarified some of the dlc item categories
\+ added 6 location on the stranger/dreamworld
\* split the dreamworld location category into multiple categories named after their ingame location

standard difficulty
force progression on Solanum and Prisonner Vault
**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/nicopop/ManualOuterWildsArchipelago/compare/vE1.0.0-pre1...vE1.0.0-pre2
